Package: erudiciondb
Title: Database Configuration and Tools for Storing and Querying Scholars 
        and Scholarship
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ryan", "Raaum", , "ryan.raaum@lehman.cuny.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4723-5475"))
Description: A database schema for scholarship linked to a specific (small) set 
                of scholars along with tools for inserting, updating, 
                querying, and otherwise managing the data along with a 
                reasonable audit trail.
